properties.TITLE: Main Channel - Hudson River/General/Hazards To Navigation/Obstructions
properties.DESCRIPTION:
General/Hazards To Navigation/Obstructions

From: 2025-01-16 To: 2025-09-01

There are unburied cables and potential hazards in the vicinity of the delineated line. Mariners are advised to transit with extreme caution and avoid anchoring in the area.

Please contact Sabrina Taylor, Sr. Project Manager at, 1 (561)714-8555, Sabrina.Taylor@tdi-usa.com, or Neil Henderson, VP Marine Operations at 1 (832) 370-1106, Neil.Henderson@tdi-usa.com, for any additional information.
